title: Huawei WLC: Access Point Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/huawei
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 This check monitors the access points managed by a Huawei Wireless LAN
 Controller (WLC). One service per access point reports the AP run state,
 the management IP address, the up/down traffic and the number of currently
 associated (online) users.

 The run state is mapped via a static table. The states {fault},
 {configFailed}, {commitFailed}, {nameConflicted} and {invalid} map to
 {CRIT}; {standby} and {verMismatch} map to {WARN}; all other states are
 {OK}.

 Optional upper levels on the number of online users can be configured via
 the rule "Huawei WLC access point". The check is detected on devices whose
 sysObjectID equals .1.3.6.1.4.1.2011.2.240.6.

item:
 The name of the access point ({hwWlanApName}).

discovery:
 One service is created for each access point reported by the controller.
